high_descs: Take seven steps forward and turn right to face the island counter.
Pick up the glass back by the roll of paper towels.
Turn left for six steps, turn left and toward the counter then turn right to face the sink.
Put the glass in the sink under the faucet and fill the glass with water.
Pick up the glass of water and turn around and go to the stove and drink the water.
Open the right cabinet door and put the glass on the shelf, on the left side and shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put an empty glass in the cabinet above the store.

high_descs: Move forward to the middle of the island, turn right to face the island.
Pick up the black cup on the island.
Turn left, bring the cup to the sink on the left.
Fill the cup with water in the sink.
Bring the filled cup to cabinet above the stove, to the left.
Put the filled cup in the right cabinet above the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a filled cup in the right cabinet above the stove.

high_descs: Walk to the teapot on the counter to your right and turn right to face it when you get there.
Pick up the cup that's in front of you by the frying pan.
Turn left and walk to the sink and position yourself so you can use it.
Fill the cup with water and pick it back up.
Now turn left and walk left to the stove and stand in front of it facing it.
Open the cupboard above the stove and put the cup of water up there then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup filled with water in the cupboard.
